HEADWORD: Platitudinous
<hw>Plat`i*tu"di*nous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Abounding in
platitudes; of the nature of platitudes; uttering platitudes.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Plat`i*tu"di*nous*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
